local Serial = require "actions/Serial" local Parallel = require "actions/Parallel" local Action = require "actions/Action" local Ease = require "actions/Ease" local Do = require "actions/Do"
local Chest = require "object/Chest"
return function(self, player) if player.crashIntoWall and not GameState:isFlagSet("get_factorybot_helmet") then GameState:setFlag("get_factorybot_helmet")
local helmet = self.scene.objectLookup.Template3 for _, obj in pairs(self.scene.map.objects) do if obj.name == "Template3" and obj.x > helmet.x and obj.x < 500 and obj.sprite then helmet = obj break end end helmet.action = Serial { Ease(helmet, "y", helmet.y - 30, 5, "inout"), Do(function() helmet.sprite.sortOrderY = 0 end), Parallel { Ease(helmet, "y", helmet.y + 150, 3, "quad"), Ease(helmet.sprite.transform, "sx", 2, 5, "quad"), Ease(helmet.sprite.transform, "sy", 2, 5, "quad"), Ease(helmet.sprite.color, 4, 255, 5, "quad"), }, Do(function() local inst = Chest( self.scene, {name="objects"}, {name="bothead", x=helmet.x, y=helmet.y, width=64, height=32, properties = { sprite = "art/sprites/factorybothelmet.png", defaultAnim = "idleright", disappearOnGrabbed = true, BotHead = 1}}) self.scene:addObject(inst) inst:postInit() helmet:remove() end) } end end
